tool_input.description: Get summary of changed files vs main

tool_input.command:
gh pr create --title "feat: #4 - New agent" --body "$(cat <<'EOF'
## Summary

- Adds a new `documenter` agent that generates documentation for completed features as the final step in the team workflow
- Updates the `team-lead` agent to invoke the documenter after all builders finish and validators confirm everything works
- Adds E2E test command for the documenter agent

## Implementation Plan

See: [specs/issue-4-adw-1d7283ec-sdlc_planner-add-documenter-agent.md](specs/issue-4-adw-1d7283ec-sdlc_planner-add-documenter-agent.md)

## Key Changes

- `.kiro/agents/documenter.json` — new documenter agent config
- `.kiro/agents/documenter-prompt.md` — documenter agent prompt
- `.kiro/agents/team-lead-prompt.md` — updated to include documenter as final workflow step
- `.kiro/agents/team-lead.json` — updated agent config
- `README.md` — updated to document the new agent and workflow position
- `.claude/commands/e2e/test_documenter_agent.md` — E2E test for documenter agent

## Workflow Position

```
builder(s) → validator (per task) → ... → final validator → documenter
```

The documenter runs last so it documents what was actually built, with real file paths and APIs, after validation has confirmed the code works.

Closes #4

ADW: 1d7283ec
EOF
)" --base main
